flowchart TD
    A[Admin opens assignment submissions list] --> B[Select submission]
    B --> C[Load submission detail and video]
    C --> D[Review assignment]
    D --> E{Decision?}
    E -->|Approve| F[Set status approved]
    E -->|Reject| G[Enter feedback]
    G --> H[Set status rejected]
    F --> I[Trigger approved email if enabled]
    H --> J[Trigger rejected email if enabled]
    I --> K[Student sees updated assignment status]
    J --> K